<h4><a href="https://www.designboom.com/design/nendo-marsotto-edizioni-brera-showroom-09-28-2020/">Nendo 为展厅设计趣味大理石立面</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1369773" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/nendo_marsotto_showroom_brera_milan_designboom03_1.jpg" alt="" width="818" height="545" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/nendo_marsotto_showroom_brera_milan_designboom03_1.jpg 818w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/nendo_marsotto_showroom_brera_milan_designboom03_1-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/nendo_marsotto_showroom_brera_milan_designboom03_1-768x512.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 818px) 100vw, 818px" /></p>
<p>Designboom 消息，Nendo 近日为意大利家具品牌 Marsotto 设计了位于米兰的展厅。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1369772" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/nendo_marsotto_showroom_brera_milan_designboom02_1.jpg" alt="" width="818" height="545" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/nendo_marsotto_showroom_brera_milan_designboom02_1.jpg 818w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/nendo_marsotto_showroom_brera_milan_designboom02_1-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/nendo_marsotto_showroom_brera_milan_designboom02_1-768x512.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 818px) 100vw, 818px" /></p>
<p>该展厅的立面设计尤其有趣，Nendo 在大理石中创造了一个「凹陷」，看起来就像是柔软的材质被人戳了一下后，正在缓慢地恢复原形。这个「凹陷」可用作休息空间，行人路过也可坐在上面休息。</p>
